.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, camping, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, drama
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, pakistani
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, indie, rock
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, tennis
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the pakistani and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching drama movies and the fan of rock##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola        | tea      |
| Hobby          | camping    | reading       | hiking  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | documentary | crime    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | argentine   | dutch    |
| Music-Genre           | indie      | r&b  | rock      |
| Sport         | tennis    | rowing      | biathlon |

