.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, plum, pumpkin
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, traveling, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, punk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, august, july
3 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, snake
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, fanta
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's birthday is in july and the owner of the cat##2
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the owner of the snake is the fan of folk##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person eating nectarine##2
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the fan of folk is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | nectarine  | plum    | pumpkin   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | writing | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | folk    | classical |
| Birthday   | july    | august  | november  |
| Pet           | ferret     | snake   | cat       |
| Beverage     | iced-tea | coffee     | fanta       |

