3. the pall-mall-smoker is the argentine##1
4. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the nigerian is on the right of the colombian##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person eating radish and the aristoff-smoker##2
9. the person who likes amber is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Color      | fuchsia      | ebony     | amber      |
| Food          | radish     | apple     | cucumber     |
| Hobby         | chess      | skydiving | gardening    |
