.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, mirinda
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, green, brown
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, pop
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, june, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
2. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the helicopter and the owner of the snake##2
3. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the fan of disco##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | coffee   | juice      |
| Color   | green | brown  | pink  |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | dubstep  | pop        |
| Pet           | snake       | rabbit   | guinea-pig |
| Birthday         | june      | april | november   |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram     | helicopter |

 